seo.title: All programs from ABC Kids
seo.description: Watch all your favourite ABC Kids programs on ABC iview. Full of lots of fun TV programs to help your kids grown and learn in an advertising-free space.

items.title: ABC KIDS Live Stream: 5:00am to 7:30pm AEDT
items.seriesTitle: ABC KIDS Live Stream: 5:00am to 7:30pm AEDT
items.description: ABC KIDS is now streamed live on iview! Watch your favourite ABC KIDS programs anytime, anywhere, on your computer, tablet or smartphone. This stream is available 5am  7.30pm AEDT and will reflect the ABC KIDS NSW schedule
items.availability: Watching this stream will consume up to 700 MB per hour.

items.title: Peppa Pig
items.description: The pre-school adventures of a cheeky and slightly bossy little pig called Peppa, who lives with her mummy and daddy and little brother George. Sometimes these adventures involve a few tears but they always end happily.

items.title: Play School Art Time
items.description: Play School Art Time is an action-packed series that celebrates creativity, curiosity and all things arty! Set in a magical art studio, the Art Crew join presenters Zindzi and Matt to create and explore the wonders of art.

items.title: Bluey
items.description: Bluey is an inexhaustible six year-old Blue Heeler dog, who loves to play and turns everyday family life into extraordinary adventures, developing her imagination as well as her mental, physical and emotional resilience.

items.title: Rusty Rivets
items.description: Rusty and best buds Ruby and Botasaur return to invent and innovate their way out of every jam by repurposing spare parts and found objects into the most awesome contraptions ever!

items.title: Kiri and Lou
items.description: In a forest of cut-out paper with creatures made of clay, Kiri and Lou invites children to learn about kindness, empathy and how to get along. Together they navigate a forest of feelings with laughter, song and adventure.

items.title: Sesame Street
items.description: Join Big Bird, Oscar, Elmo, Bert, Cookie Monster, the Count and many other characters to learn the alphabet and to count with Count von Count, but most of all just have a good time.

items.title: Kiddets
items.description: Five young space cadets in training at a play school space academy on planet WotWot will learn all the skills they need to embark on a mission to a new world under the watchful eye of SpottyWot and DottyWot.

items.title: Hey Duggee
items.description: 'The Squirrel Club' is run by a big friendly dog called Duggee - a place where kids take part in all kinds of activities, have adventures and earn activity badges all along the way.

items.title: PJ Masks
items.description: When the city sleeps, Connor, Amaya & Greg's PJs magically transform the kids into superheroes - here comes Catboy, Owlette & Gekko! Watch out nighttime baddies - the PJ Masks are on their way, into the night to save the day!

items.title: Charlie And Lola
items.description: The adventures of seven year-old Charlie and his feisty little sister Lola in this fresh, exuberant, delightfully witty animation.

items.title: Octonauts Special: The Over Under Adventure
items.showTitle: Octonauts Special: The Over Under Adventure
items.displayTitle: Octonauts Special: The Over Under Adventure
items.description: The mission to explore Antarctica becomes a desperate rescue as a group of sea stars and urchins is threatened by a rare underwater icicle that can freeze creatures on the seabed.
items.availability: This program was published 2 weeks ago, available until 5:40pm on 26 Aug 2019.

items.title: Ready, Steady, Wiggle!
items.description: Anthony, Emma, Lachy and Simon engage, entertain and inform children with their catchy songs and delightful characters.

items.title: Dinosaur Train
items.description: The show is set in a whimsically realistic, prehistoric world of jungles, swamps, active volcanoes and oceans, all teeming with dinosaur and animal life, and connected by a shining train line known as the Dinosaur Train.

items.title: Nella the Princess Knight
items.description: Follow the adventures of Nella, a brave princess who turns into a princess knight.

items.title: Thomas And Friends
items.description: Join Thomas And Friends in Big World! Big Adventures! as they travel the tracks on the island of Sodor, under the direction of the Fat Controller.
